===學名藥價格飆升===
[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]在2015年12月的社論中指出，"藥品價格無緣無故被拉到天文數字的高價，原因無非就是藥廠希望獲得最大利潤"，社論中特別點名{{link-en|Vyera 製藥|Vyera Pharmaceuticals}}和{{link-en|Bausch Health|Bausch Health}}兩家藥業，在製造和銷售他們有獨家管理權的學名藥，兩家藥業把售價大幅度提高的行徑，在[[製藥產業|製藥產業]]內外均受到廣泛的譴責。<ref name="NYT-20151219">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/opinion/sunday/no-justification-for-high-drug-prices.html|title=No Justification for High Drug Prices|date=19 December 2015|work=New York Times|author=The Editorial Board|accessdate=20 December 2015}}</ref>
 
[[美國衛生和公共服務部|美國衛生和公共服務部]]（DHHS）和國會參眾兩院為此事分別舉行公開會議和聽證會，以調查這項{{link-en|哄抬價格|Price gouging}}的行為。<ref>US Senate Special Committee on Aging. [http://www.aging.senate.gov/press-releases/collins-mccaskill-open-senate-investigation-into-rx-drug-pricing-announce-intention-to-hold-hearings Collins, McCaskill open Senate investigation into Rx drug pricing, announce intention to hold hearings. November 4, 2015. Accessed 4 January 2016.]</ref>2017年4月，[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]打算成為第一個州去授予[[州檢察長|州檢察長]]權力，以起訴大幅提高藥品價格的藥廠。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/politics/bs-md-drug-price-gouging-20170410-story.html|title=Maryland General Assembly passes bill aimed at drug 'price gouging'|last=Duncan|first=Ian|work=baltimoresun.com|access-date=2017-05-01|language=en-US}}</ref>2018年4月，[[美國聯邦第四巡迴上訴法院|美國聯邦第四巡迴上訴法院]]分庭裁定，馬里蘭州這項法律違反[[美國憲法|美國憲法]]中的《{{link-en|休眠商業條款|Dormant Commerce Clause}}》。<ref>{{cite journal |first=|last=Note|title=Recent Case: Fourth Circuit Invalidates Maryland Statute Regulating Price Gouging in the Sale of Generic Drugs|volume=132 |journal=[[Harvard_Law_Review|Harv. L. Rev.]] |page=1748 | url=https://harvardlawreview.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1748-1755_Online.pdf|year=2019}}.</ref><ref>{{cite court |litigants=Association for Accessible Medicines v. Frosh|vol= 887 |reporter=F.3d|opinion= 664 |court=4th Cir.|date=2018|url=https://scholar.google.com/scholar_case?case=17880672085993330281|accessdate=}}</ref>
 
藥品受到影響的例子包括{{link-en|艾筆腎上腺素注射筆|epinephrine autoinjector}}（簡稱EpiPen）和[[胰島素|胰島素]]。<ref>[https://www.statnews.com/2019/02/19/no-generic-insulin-who-is-to-blame/ 'Everyone is at fault': With insulin prices skyrocketing, there’s plenty of blame to go around]</ref>在2011年至2016年之間，EpiPen唯一的競爭對手是[[邁蘭|邁蘭]]藥業的產品，EpiPen的價格因此被拉高近400％，被迫購買的消費者購買兩包EpiPen，必須支付600美元或更多現金。<ref name="#1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.goodrx.com/blog/generic-epipen-is-still-expensive-heres-how-you-can-save/|title=Generic EpiPen Is Still Expensive - Here's How You Can Save - GoodRx|date=2019-05-24|work=The GoodRx Prescription Savings Blog|access-date=2019-10-23|language=en-US}}</ref>由於公眾的強烈抗議和要求，邁蘭藥業和[[梯瓦|梯瓦]]製藥後來宣佈為EpiPen製造學名藥產品。然而，對於患者而言，價格仍然很高，而且要用現金支付。兩包自動注射器的學名藥腎上腺素的現金價格平均約為350美元，如果患者的醫療保險不涵蓋這種學名藥，他們需要其主治醫師代表他們向保險公司提交申訴信件，爭取折讓。<ref name="#1"/>

===川普總統行政命令===
